{"tid":905441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【metoo】律政司高級檢控官，涉三單非禮，墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-11-17T06:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T16:30:32.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce80bc18797842875d2282301b835b16be49008","tid":905441,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"【13:01】墮樓死者為懷疑涉嫌非禮的高級檢控官王永森<br />\n<br />\n大角嘴海帆道11號凱帆軒2座，早上10時左右，一名40餘歲男子從高處墮下平台。保安員致電報警，但經救援人員檢驗，證實事主已告身亡。警方正調查死者身份及墮樓原因。據悉，死者為律政司隸屬刑事檢控科的男高級檢控官王永森。"},{"pid":"e5d99c983bd072a3a35375080e49f66190853841","tid":905441,"uid":155431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"e008fcda4e0bfcec49aa36952cad6583294c4a62","tid":905441,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"#medied"},{"pid":"244ae3f7c45c78d904d816838d78ae3be134ace5","tid":905441,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"他被指在過去一年間多次在辦公室走廊以肩膊或手肘撞向迎面女同事的胸部，惹起部份女檢控官不滿，至今年5月18日報警。警方最終於6月30日將他拘捕。"},{"pid":"34b54e30b8aa2d34fa9913695eddd966ca6b1805","tid":905441,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c382684aca0271be4f7b210080eaa640ef68b8","tid":905441,"uid":178800,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"呢個抵死<br />\n咁中意搵手肘撞波<br />\n而家無顏面對現實<br />\n一了百了"},{"pid":"fdc82a6467999b23f3210d17ef3b76ca75d684ca","tid":905441,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ac0570977a6a7ecd0452657878c7666bf8e638","tid":905441,"uid":99642,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"港女有波？"},{"pid":"8cba35e8a3348ab4644b197933daa7461